  "description": "A method to perform biology experiments at home",
  "body_html": "<p>In my last <a href=\"https://chillphysicsenjoyer.substack.com/p/culturing-yeast-for-independent-science\">post</a>, I tried to grow yeast colonies at different concentrations. I wanted to find the sweet spot that would give me an easy countable number of colonies, to make it amenable for further testing. After three days of growing, here are the results!</p><p>The stock solution - too many colonies. </p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!CBcx!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ae23458-8e30-4c72-8e41-7a99ba86cfad_4032x3024.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!CBcx!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ae23458-8e30-4c72-8e41-7a99ba86cfad_4032x3024.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!CBcx!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ae23458-8e30-4c72-8e41-7a99ba86cfad_4032x3024.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!CBcx!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ae23458-8e30-4c72-8e41-7a99ba86cfad_4032x3024.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!CBcx!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ae23458-8e30-4c72-8e41-7a99ba86cfad_4032x3024.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!CBcx!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ae23458-8e3